    • Configuration

      public Configuration(int totalTickets, int ticketReleaseRate, int customerRetrievalRate, int maxTicketCapacity)
      Constructs a Configuration object with the specified parameters.
      Parameters:
      totalTickets - the total number of tickets available.
      ticketReleaseRate - the rate at which tickets are released.
      customerRetrievalRate - the rate at which customers retrieve tickets.
      maxTicketCapacity - the maximum capacity of tickets that can be stored.
